00:41:19,208 --> 00:41:20,917
Then you can play with it forever.

490
00:41:22,625 --> 00:41:24,458
Come on, you'll have fun.

491
00:41:24,542 --> 00:41:25,917
Leave my hand alone!

492
00:41:27,542 --> 00:41:29,417
Come on, stop resisting.

