00:41:33,167 --> 00:41:34,667
Dashrath.

494
00:41:36,875 --> 00:41:38,833
Dashrath, leave him.

495
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:01,500
Don't you trust me?

496
00:42:19,292 --> 00:42:24,292
Phaguniya.
O', Phaguniya! You are my life. Life.

497
00:42:26,458 --> 00:42:30,875
